4 receiver, estate, trust, or any other group or combination of
5 groups acting as a unit.
6 (u) "Preservation" means projects that involve rehabilitation
7 of existing housing units or the adaptive re-use of an existing
8 building.
9 (v) "Qualified project" means a qualified low-income building
